{"id": "1451983219531583610", "channel_id": "1451983219531583610", "type": 0, "author_id": "1302298693369856000", "author_name": "flim_of_life_burst", "author_bot": false, "content": "Note: Another parcel will be delivered later during the lunch break!\n\n⫘⫘⫘ˎˊ˗ ·˖✶ ☽ ☼ ☾ ✶˖· ˗ˏˋ⫘⫘⫘\n\nKeeper, \n\nI once asked whether, when Kadas fell, you might be willing to travel with me to my distant dwelling, remember?\nThere’s no need to wait for such a vague and far-off moment. For this one day only, the Gateway to Forever stands open to you. You will have the chance to visit the Grand Court, ascend the tower, and join the feasting of the kindred… Bring nothing with you—unless you’ve prepared a birthday gift for me.\nSame place as always.\n\nPrince Sun-Chaser\n\n✧⫘⫘⫘ˎˊ˗ ·˖✶ ☽ ☼ ☾ ✶˖· ˗ˏˋ⫘⫘⫘\n\nKeeper, \n\nI rarely speak of my mother to anyone.\nI have never forgotten her. Humans cannot endure the union with a god. From that moment on, her body was ravaged by the backlash of power—fevers, and the body slowly turning strange. That was the price she paid.\nShe disappeared. I don’t know where she went. But before that, every year on my birthday, she would celebrate it with me in the way of human kindness. I’ve kept that habit to this day.\nAt university, I don’t really have anyone close. Come and see me. You are my friend. I want to share this moment with you.\n\nSolvarg", "timestamp": "2025-12-20T17:02:56.080000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1451983220517109791", "filename": "IMG_9344.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 598389, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1451983219531583610/1451983220517109791/IMG_9344.jpg?ex=6a00ba40&is=69ff68c0&hm=9c4a74b00358536bfacc747778f341f9e2821e20465a4aeff98418c89f148f31&"}, {"id": "1451983224388456668", "filename": "IMG_9345.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 472685, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1451983219531583610/145198